# CardioDil AI — Environment Variables Reference
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your real keys
# .env.local is gitignored and never committed
# This file IS committed — it contains no real secrets
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HOW TO GET EACH KEY
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── SUPABASE ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used for: all database operations, auth, RLS
# Project name: cardiodil-ai (in your Rohimaya Pro org)
#
# How to get:
# 1. Go to https://supabase.com/dashboard
# 2. Open your cardiodil-ai project
# 3. Click Settings in the left sidebar
# 4. Click API
# 5. Copy Project URL → paste as EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
# 6. Copy anon public key → paste as EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# Never use the service_role key in a mobile app
#
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://yourproject.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

# ── ANTHROPIC ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used for: Dil agent, Meal Vision food analysis, weekly insight generation
# Model: claude-sonnet-4-5 (vision + conversation), claude-haiku (quick confirmations)
#
# How to get:
# 1. Go to https://console.anthropic.com
# 2. Click API Keys in the left sidebar
# 3. Click Create Key
# 4. Name it: cardiodil-mobile
# 5. Copy the key immediately — it is only shown once
#
EXPO_PUBLIC_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── ELEVENLABS ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used for: Dil voice output (text-to-speech)
# Dil speaks to Prasad — warm, calm, clinical tone
#
# How to get your API key:
# 1. Go to https://elevenlabs.io
# 2. Click your profile icon → Profile + API Key
# 3. Copy your API key
#
# How to get your Voice ID:
# 1. Go to https://elevenlabs.io/voice-lab
# 2. Create or clone a voice for Dil
#    Recommended: start with "Adam" or "Antoni" as a base
#    Adjust stability to 0.75, similarity boost to 0.85 for clinical warmth
# 3. Click the voice → copy the Voice ID from the URL or settings
#
EXPO_PUBLIC_ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=sk_...
EXPO_PUBLIC_ELEVENLABS_VOICE_ID=21m00Tcm4TlvDq8ikWAM

# ── NUTRITIONIX ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Used for: Brand Intelligence chain (restaurant items and branded food fallback)
# Query order: Open Food Facts → USDA → Nutritionix
# Nutritionix is the paid fallback — only called if the first two return no result
#
# How to get:
# 1. Go to https://www.nutritionix.com/business/api
# 2. Click Get API Access
# 3. Select the Nutritionix Track API plan (free tier available)
# 4. After signup go to your dashboard
# 5. Copy App ID → paste as EXPO_PUBLIC_NUTRITIONIX_APP_ID
# 6. Copy API Key → paste as EXPO_PUBLIC_NUTRITIONIX_API_KEY
#
EXPO_PUBLIC_NUTRITIONIX_APP_ID=your_app_id
EXPO_PUBLIC_NUTRITIONIX_API_KEY=your_api_key

# ── USDA FOODDATA CENTRAL ─────────────────────────────────
# Used for: whole and unprocessed ingredient nutrition data
# Free, government data, gold standard for whole foods
# Open Food Facts is checked first for branded/packaged items
# USDA is checked for whole ingredients (salmon, brown rice, broccoli, etc.)
#
# How to get:
# 1. Go to https://fdc.nal.usda.gov/api-guide.html
# 2. Click Get an API Key (top right)
# 3. Fill in your name and email
# 4. Your key is emailed to you instantly — no approval needed
#
EXPO_PUBLIC_USDA_API_KEY=DEMO_KEY

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NOTES ON OPEN FOOD FACTS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Open Food Facts requires NO API key
# It is free, open source, and community verified
# CardioDil queries it directly at https://world.openfoodfacts.org/api/v2
# No environment variable needed
# It is always checked FIRST in the Brand Intelligence chain
# for any branded or packaged food item

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# BRAND INTELLIGENCE QUERY ORDER (reminder)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Open Food Facts — branded packaged foods (no key needed)
# 2. USDA FoodData Central — whole unprocessed ingredients
# 3. Nutritionix — restaurant items and final fallback
# If all three return no result → Dil asks user to read the label
# Dil NEVER estimates nutrition for a branded product
